{"tid":1765112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香城online攻略】和理非、勇武外第三職業：和你勇","createTime":"2019-12-01T15:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T14:50:59.000Z","uid":227858,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3ef65c1e19c1dc045aa0dfa214dfacafa02c219","tid":1765112,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:18:25.000Z","msg":"作為香城online嘅資深玩家，今日終於見到第三職業嘅出現，有d想分享下戰術。<br />\n<br />\n首先定義唔同職業嘅功能同優劣：<br />\n【勇武】：<br />\n定義：主攻手<br />\n優點：高戰力，高傷害，人數少，可以無視空氣污染<br />\n缺點：容易受boss集火，一唔小心被boss捉中就會強制封號10年<br />\n<br />\n【和理非】：<br />\n定義：運輸/物資/哨兵<br />\n優點：人多，就算中boss嘅捉人大技都未必封號/最多48小時就可以再度上線，湊人數<br />\n缺點：0防禦，boss一開技就走，阻住【勇武】撤退，boss一出就中恐慌debuff<br />\n<br />\n【和你勇】：<br />\n功能：盡量唔做任何可以引致封號嘅事，無裝備，有必要時企上第一排，掩護【勇武】撤退<br />\n優點：因為無做任何嘢，純屬係度企，可以以最低成本吸引boss火力<br />\n缺點：boss有不確定性，有機會比中bug嘅boss當場/後期打死，0防禦，又稱【被捕師】<br />\n<br />\n基本排陣如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SY3uOaC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSY3uOaC.jpg&h=efb27186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要點：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 有得揀唔好打陣地，呢個圖只適合一d被迫打陣地嘅副本，例如之前嘅限時大學副本</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>2. 唔該簡定職業，有齊心理準備先入副本，如果唔係就累人累物</strong><br />\n3. 基本上前進同後退要保持陣勢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4. 任何調動都係由【勇武】指揮，後排唔可以直接quit game</span><br />\n5. 【和理非】人鏈之間留空位比【勇武】走<br />\n6. 【和你勇】係要係【勇武】退後後佔據前排位置，如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ZcrQrS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ZcrQrS.jpg&h=9fd74d47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7. 【和你勇】指揮【和理非】後退，【勇武】回主城，再大家一起offline<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>祝大家早日爆機</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n聲明：本攻略僅使用於遊戲，絕不鼓勵任何現實犯法行為，強烈譴責暴徒暴力"},{"pid":"dd99e1e1f633b59a64458fa04f89db7d6d3880d7","tid":1765112,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:18:42.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫推"},{"pid":"5cb03e24cdef989f8aec6ecc26ba5c0d6df91ef0","tid":1765112,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:19:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cc6fcc6c1193ed80a6805408f7c3dc270e8b329","tid":1765112,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:19:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e221584f0f016a9acced75395d9593bdfe399304","tid":1765112,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:19:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fe7c6335c57306811f844f3d680bb0f82f7228e","tid":1765112,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:20:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5faea1da72d29fdf25ee663707cb616500905a49","tid":1765112,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:20:41.000Z","msg":"戰術post無人推？"},{"pid":"c1e9bd32cfd563f739748e1b60ac4f13222c03bd","tid":1765112,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:20:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e742e282c167a5455177f221026512f9767d855d","tid":1765112,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:21:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d4bea5e94f30dd2f3405d4428a3d01596e66f7d","tid":1765112,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:23:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9330d3638acf802d75bef4dc9f1f4723652895ef","tid":1765112,"uid":173072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:46:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔出刀咪又係送頭大會</span></span>"},{"pid":"0f56a3e06b454cdef517b5a2518c0f3a0961c545","tid":1765112,"uid":35953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"佢地唔係我boss"},{"pid":"1954fbb14f41a1dd0630b05d1404db9be5dba62d","tid":1765112,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:57:02.000Z","msg":"嗰d位勁多子彈飛嚟飛去<br />\n冇裝好易出事<br />\n<br />\n陣地的話<br />\n佢想告暴動嘅話 所有在場人士都可以告暴動<br />\n佢照樣可以的你過堂<br />\n<br />\n不過可以討論"},{"pid":"cc1521681c99d4235d95f802f43436d741a00115","tid":1765112,"uid":274999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T14:34:40.000Z","msg":"咁咪即係肉盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0e033fa9ba99ba15a3341535b8ced4b74a977d","tid":1765112,"uid":4750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T14:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d792d505dfe518cc5cf0f3d3b38e3c0b4c2a62","tid":1765112,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}